header.gameNote: MAC MEN'S TOURNAMENT PRES. BY VISITMYRTLEBEACH.COM - FINAL

videos.description: Toledos' Dylan Alderson posts up in front of the basket, pivots backward and fakes a shot then pivots back toward the basket and sinks the clean layup while faking out a Buffalo defender.
videos.headline: Alderson uses the pivot foot of glory to beat Buffalo defender

videos.description: Dontay Caruthers drives to the basket and sinks a crafty layup with a group of Toledo defenders in his face.
videos.headline: Caruthers beats 3 Toledo defenders for impressive layup

videos.description: Wes Clark grabs a defensive rebound and drives the length of the floor before somehow finding teammate Ikenna Smart with multiple defenders in his face who then slams it down.
videos.headline: Sensational Buffalo pass leads to monster slam

videos.description: Wes Clark beats a Toledo defender 1-on-1 with a nice spin move then easily sinks the layup for the Bulls.
videos.headline: Clark's sweet spin move helps extend Buffalo's lead

videos.description: Toledo's Willie Jackson punches the stanchion after grabbing an offensive rebound then getting fouled.
videos.headline: Jackson gives the stanchion a knockout punch

videos.description: Nick Perkins fights his way for 2 points despite the efforts of a group of Toledo defenders draped on him.
videos.headline: Buffalo's Perkins Bulls his way for 2

videos.description: Buffalo's Nate Oats and Wes Clark reflect on their MAAC championship victory and speak on the spectacular play of Clark who had a difficult journey to become a conference champion.
videos.headline: Coach Oats says Clark has been 'perfect for us'
